Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-- the harshest sea ruled \Nby the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They landed on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an island with two parts, one \Nburning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy learned about the hideous experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,performed by Caesar Clown, the Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and headed off to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the clan split up. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are footprints, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it an animal? If it's a \Nhuman, he must be a Giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two beast-looking creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law? The Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're on a snow-capped \Nmountain so it must be them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Snow Mountain Killers - stalking \Nout from deep in the snowstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Brownbeard, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is also on our kill list.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, you didn't harm \Nmy friends, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took Nami with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Save Nami! Luffy's Fight on \Nthe Snow-Capped Mountains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They kidnapped Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they were very big,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice they were there until
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they appeared in front of my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, it was centaurs and now, beast men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a bunch of strange creatures here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they were waiting for their \Nchance to attack us somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't come here to save Brown-gator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like their main purpose \Nwas to kill us and take the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, they killed Brownbeard \Nat the Master's command.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were supposed to be on the same side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard admired him so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master was our warm-hearted savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Master guy is a very twisted person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let these kids go \Nback to such an evil person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help worrying about \NNami in Franky's body, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what they're gonna do to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll get her back at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, look after those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my body that they took!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, I can't fight like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the bean that you \Neat when you transform
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yourself into a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a bean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rumble Ball is a power drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you can control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle it with my super spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it to me! There's no time to argue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! It was in this \Npocket the whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it was. It's Chopper's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. You can become a monster \Nfor just three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fight after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if possible, transform into Kung \NFu Boost like I did earlier and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buber!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Franky! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you attacking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! He's out of control as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is there much point to Franky going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After running wild, he won't \Nbe able to move for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he's not gonna be helpful at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, he's going to be in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:56.28,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,CAESAR'S LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where he got it but \Nthis "Cyborg" Franky guy has...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Vegapunk's laser weapon \Nmounted in his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make good use of Vegapunk's invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I chop his body up and \Ntake the laser system out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he will be useless. Get \Nthe incinerator ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with the Navy \Nidiots who came to steal the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ambushed them successfully but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What are they?!\N--Humans?! No, horses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't get beaten that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is no good!\N--Nowhere to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to change tactics!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to seize the ship in full force!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan... I mean, Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle is out of control now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're having a hard fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the perfect opportunity to test it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's great! Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact the centaurs who are on patrol now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell all the other soldiers \Nevacuate if they want to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:31.61,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE MOUNTAIN BEHIND THE LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Let me go, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you guys?! You perverts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm pretty and have a good figure
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you couldn't help kidnapping me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this guy talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be a queer. That's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna pay for this! \NLuffy won't tolerate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you two get your asses kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet for a moment. Noisy \Npeople like you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the weapons that are \Nmounted in your body are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we give them to the Master, \Nour reward will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ROCK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:27.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold today as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:31.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SCOTCH
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:35.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE SNOW MOUNTAIN KILLERS \NTHE YETI COOL BROTHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.59,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Then put some clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our rifles are like cannons to you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have poison gas canisters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can beat us because \Nwe don't show ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said your friend will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll come. We \Nset a trap to lure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can't help following \Nfootprints in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Footprints! Footprints! How helpful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are pretty easy to follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Franky, I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The footprints end there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Chopper... No, Franky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! They're around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we, Scotch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! He didn't notice there \Nwas a cliff. He is so careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are spikes at the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:13:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Die in vain.\N--Get skewered by the Ice Spikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armament Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. He's a little \Ntrickier than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Stamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool. We know these mountains \Nlike our own backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many places \Nthat we can hide ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE BURNING LANDS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place that the Master mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a huge building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of eerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This door is the one, right? \NOkay, let me open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tight! Guys, give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we've been told not to go \Nanywhere near here, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay to open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master was the one who told us \Nthat and he wants us to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't trust the Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stop complaining and lend a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They move so fast even though they're so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dead-end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste to use this power only
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,defensively just letting the \Nbullets bounce randomly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Rayleigh said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said I should focus on redirecting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every single one of them \Nback with twice the force!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fire Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you struggling with him more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they having a falling \Nout now? Screw them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just see if you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Icy mountains are filled \Nwith potential weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! The tip of an \Nicy mountain is gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Franky! Look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other one is right there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choke on this KYP gas canister that \Nwill make you drunk in a second
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and drop dead like your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did something useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! That was great, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Elephant Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used one of his most daring attack there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Franky and Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Chopper to treat you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. We know these \Nmountains like our own backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't catch up with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can reach way farther than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He's like a monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Since it's a huge mountain \Nrange, it'd be a pain if I lose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're the free-loader--- \NTrafalgar Law, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chased by Straw Hat Luffy and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter Shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Hey you, give me back my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.33,0:22:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you save Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I came here to talk to you \Nabout something, Straw Hat-ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you arrived on \Nthis island by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.97,0:22:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is an important key \Nlying somewhere on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.81,0:22:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that can wreak havoc in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two ways to \Nsurvive in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either by living under the Four Emperors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or going against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I guess you're not a kind of person \Nwho wants to work under someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I want to stay as a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we have to form an alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.86,0:22:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.09,0:23:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.05,0:23:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you and I join forces, maybe we can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to bring down one of the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.20,0:23:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law declares to defeat the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and the others can't help but be hesitant by the frightening details...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy's answer surprises not only his crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Law, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.59,0:23:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Caesar was also setting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a terrible plan in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Formed! Luffy and Law's Pirate Alliance!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.93,0:23:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
